text: Ærest to Dumeltun eastan on Esingburnan.
Ðanon suðan on Esingburnan westweardes andlang dices.
Ðæt swa up on gerihte on Dagan oran.
Ðæt swa andlang stæðbroces in gemære dic.
Ðæt swa of secgmære estrihte in Esingburnan on Dyrna ford.
Ðonne sindon ðis ða gemære æt Pidwyllan.
Of crundelum suðrihte andlang hricges on tittan dune.
Of tittan dune west on cealdan wyllan.
And ðeder hyrð inn an haga on port.
And swa andlang Pidwellan up oð crundelu.
